data.description: Beautiful, well-cared for spacious home with two living spaces and two dining spaces.  Three good-sized bedrooms and full bath are on second level.  From the sliding door to the backyard, a lovely covered patio greets you, with a full privacy fence and 10 x 12 storage shed. Updates galore since 2009:  Roof, Windows, heat, hot water tank, exterior doors, flooring, kitchen, baths, light fixtures, double-wide concrete driveway with additional parking pad.  This move-in ready home is just what you’ve been looking for!
